      "source": [
        "### Right-to-left execution\n",
        "\n",
        "If you try the following code, what do you think will happen?\n",
        "\n",
        "```python\n",
        "a = 7\n",
        "a = a*2\n",
        "print( a )\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "Try it out in your own notebook!\n"
      ]
